Qt Hldplugin version 3.2.2 is a bugfix release.

The most important changes are listed in this document. For a complete
list of changes, see the Git log for the Qt Hldplugin sources that
you can check out from the public Git repository. For example:

git clone git://gitorious.org/qt-hldplugin/qt-hldplugin.git
git log --cherry-pick --pretty=oneline v3.2.1..v3.2.2

Editing
   * Fixed crash with Toggle Comment Selection (QTHLDPLUGINBUG-12987)
   * Fixed that Select All set the cursor to top of document
     (QTHLDPLUGINBUG-12860)

Help
   * Fixed crash with help index locator filter

Managing and Building Projects
   * Fixed that closing Qt Hldplugin while Projects mode is active lost all
     session data (QTHLDPLUGINBUG-13098)

CMake Projects
   * Fixed crash when selecting make target (QTHLDPLUGINBUG-13129)

Generic Projects
   * Fixed that include paths were not updated when files are added
     (QTHLDPLUGINBUG-12873)

Version Control Systems
   * ClearCase
      * Fixed that reserved checkout was performed even when unchecking the checkbox
        (QTHLDPLUGINBUG-12847)

Platform Specific

OS X
   * Fixed issues with Xcode 6
   * Fixed that Ctrl+P when editing collided with Perforce version control shortcuts
     even when not using Perforce (QTHLDPLUGINBUG-13092)

iOS
   * Fixed issues with Xcode 6
